      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "import numpy as np\n\n# Daily step count data for 30 days\nsteps = np.array([\n7500, 8200, 9100, 10000, 12000, 6800, 7400, 11000, 9500, 10200,\n8700, 7600, 8900, 9200, 13000, 14000, 9800, 10500, 11200, 9700,\n8800, 7900, 10100, 11500, 12300, 9500, 8700, 9200, 10800, 9900\n])\n\n# Key statistics\ntotal_steps = np.sum(steps)\naverage_steps = np.mean(steps)\nmax_steps = np.max(steps)\nmin_steps = np.min(steps)\n\nprint(\"Total Steps in the Month:\", total_steps)\nprint(\"Average Steps per Day:\", average_steps)\nprint(\"Maximum Steps:\", max_steps)\nprint(\"Minimum Steps:\", min_steps)\n\n# High activity days (threshold = 10000)\nthreshold = 10000\nhigh_activity_days = np.where(steps > threshold)\n\nprint(\"\\nHigh Activity Days (Steps > 10000):\")\nprint(high_activity_days[0] + 1)\n\n# Trend analysis\ntrend = np.diff(steps)\n\nprint(\"\\nDaily Change in Steps:\")\nprint(trend)",
